@baseUrl = http://localhost:5199
@contentType = application/json

### 1) Admin ile login (seed verisi)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@raporax.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### 2) Hatalı şifre — 401 beklenir
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@raporax.com",
  "password": "YanlisParola!"
}

###

### 3) Var olmayan kullanıcı — 401 beklenir (aynı mesaj, bilgi sızdırmaz)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "yok@raporax.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### 4) Validation hatası — 400 beklenir
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "gecersiz-email",
  "password": "k"
}

###
